issue.title: Track Mechanics
issue.body:
Calculate percentage of the track that the player has traversed around a lap.

Must be able to detect where a lap starts.

- [x] Spline object system
- [x] Kart position tracking
- [x] Lap counting

issue.title: Input Manager Settings
issue.body:
Have separate controls for each player - set to the same values but get the input from separate joysticks.

- [x] Throttle
- [x] Steering
- [x] Action (Fire Pickup)

issue.title: Kart Physics
issue.body:
A kart should:

- [x] Drive forwards/backwards
- [x] Turn left and right
- [x] Have gravity (*how will slopes be handled?*)

issue.title: Basic Track/Circuit
issue.body:
Simple, flat, oval shape with overlapping spline of the shape.

Used for testing. Not the final track to demo
